"H1",{"class":"Headingstyled__StyledHeading-sc-1tmxkna-0 iyuLkD"},"Find refuse and recycling dates and your local councillors"],["DIV",{"class":"meta__content"},["SPAN",{"class":"Datestyled__StyledDate-sc-1ygulc4-0 kovpYO"},[[2,83]],[[2,84]],"17 Jun 2025"],["DIV",{"class":"social__share SocialSharestyled__StyledSocialShare-sc-9j7llu-0 kehnrU"},[[2,88]],["UL",{},[[2,94]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"mailto:?subject=Find%20refuse%20and%20recycling%20dates%20and%20your%20local%20councillors&body=/find","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer"},[[2,96]],[[2,98]]]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?href='/find","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer"},[[2,102]],[[2,104]]]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=/find&text=Find%20refuse%20and%20recycling%20dates%20and%20your%20local%20councillors","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer"},[[2,108]],[[2,110]]]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=/find&title=Find%20refuse%20and%20recycling%20dates%20and%20your%20local%20councillors","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer"},[[2,114]],[[2,116]]]],[[2,130]]]]]],["DIV",{"class":"HtmlRaw-s2hey9-0 eOtthb text__block"},["H2",{},"Refuse and recycling collection dates"],"\n",["P",{},"To find out when your refuse and recycling will be collected use the search feature below. You can select to view or download a calendar for 1, 2, 3 months or all scheduled dates."],"\n",["P",{},"We are no longer producing annual waste collection calendars. This allows us to keep collection dates as up to date as possible and cater for any unexpected changes in collections dates, for example, due to weather conditions or other unprecedented circumstances."],"\n",["P",{},"We will continue to provide information on changes to scheduled collection dates through our website, social media, yellow road signs and bin hangers over the Christmas and new year period."],"\n",["P",{},"The easiest and most environmentally friendly way to view your collection dates is to use the search feature below. Please only print if absolutely necessary."],"\n",["P",{},"Please note that you will not be able to search for business collection dates using this form. If you are searching for a new build property, there may be a delay in your bin schedule being added."],"\n",["P",{},["STRONG",{},"Please note:"]," flat blocks are not included in the refuse / recycling search facility."]],["A",{"class":"Link-sc-1lopz1l-0 ejDSOa ButtonLinkstyled__StyledButtonLink-bmavc8-0 cjctAW button","href":"https://stevenage-self.achieveservice.com/service/my_bin_collection_schedule","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer"},"Find your refuse / recycling collection dates",["SPAN",{"class":"visuallyHidden__VisuallyHidden-sc-1q0qjf3-0 cgNNHv"}," - opens new window"],["svg",{"class":"ExtSvg-sc-19z86si-0 jBRYNo external-link-icon","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"16","height":"16","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"CurrentColor","stroke-linecap":"square","stroke-linejoin":"arcs"},["title",{},"External Link - opens in a new window"],["g",{"fill":"none","fill-rule":"evenodd"},["path",{"d":"M18 14v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h5M15 3h6v6M10 14L20.2 3.8"}]]]],["DIV",{"class":"HtmlRaw-s2hey9-0 eOtthb text__block"},["P",{},"If your refuse or recycling collection has been missed please see our ",["A",{"title":"Report a missed refuse or recycling collection","href":"/waste-and-recycling/missed-bins","data-nodeid":"83a3dd5f-356d-4f6a-b306-2b81b89299d8","data-nodelanguage":"en-GB","data-entryid":"bbdef965-85d2-465e-8ed0-31b3aaad4905"},"missed bins page"],"."]],["DIV",{"class":"HtmlRaw-s2hey9-0 eOtthb text__block"},["H2",{},"Local councillors"],["P",{},"If you are unsure about which ward you live in or who your local councillor is, you can find details about your local councillors and contact them."]],["A",{"class":"Link-sc-1lopz1l-0 ejDSOa ButtonLinkstyled__StyledButtonLink-bmavc8-0 cjctAW button","href":"https://stevenage-self.achieveservice.com/en/service/Find_my_councillor","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer"},"Find out who your local councillor is",["SPAN",{"class":"visuallyHidden__VisuallyHidden-sc-1q0qjf3-0 cgNNHv"}," - opens new window"],["svg",{"class":"ExtSvg-sc-19z86si-0 jBRYNo external-link-icon","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"16","height":"16","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"CurrentColor","stroke-linecap":"square","stroke-linejoin":"arcs"},["title",{},"External Link - opens in a new window"],["g",{"fill":"none","fill-rule":"evenodd"},["path",{"d":"M18 14v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h5M15 3h6v6M10 14L20.2 3.8"}]]]]],["DIV",{"class":"Columnstyled__StyledColumn-sc-1aq1prz-0 cXPEcD width26 column"},["DIV",{"class":"RelatedLinksstyled__StyledRelatedLinks-kx9h9e-0 dNavki"},[[2,199]],["UL",{},["LI",{},["DIV",{"class":"flex-wrapper"},["A",{"class":"Link-sc-1lopz1l-0 fAmSU","target":"_self","href":"/tradewaste"},"Trade Waste"]]]]]]]],[[2,381]]]],[[9,29]],[[8,390]],[[8,391]],[[8,392]],[[2,386]]]],"viewport":{"width":800,"height":461},"timestamp":14660.079,"wallTime":1753094958315,"collectionTime":1.900000000372529,"resourceOverrides":[],"isMainFrame":true}}
